var Lat,Lon,Maptype


function getxy(e) {
Lat = 36.721590 - 0.012210*e.getY()
Lat = Math.round(Lat*100000)/100000
Lon = 90.465567 - 0.015023*e.getX()
Lon = -Math.round(Lon*100000)/100000
}

function popit(e) {

getxy(e)
popup = "nearby.php?me=Q&melat=" + Lat + "&melon=" + Lon;
window.open(popup,"nearby", 'width=300,height=300,scrollbars=yes,menubar=yes');
}

function thd() {

myLayer = new DynLayer(null,20,60,590,144,null,null,1,'tmp.gif')
myListener = new EventListener(DynAPI.document)
myListener.onmousemove=function(e) {
getxy(e)
window.defaultStatus = ' '
window.status = " " + Lat + " " + Lon
}
myListener.onmousedown=function(e) {
popit(e)
}
myLayer.addEventListener(myListener)
DynAPI.document.addChild(myLayer)

}
